<pre>
タイトル: <font size = 5>Coldain BracerのLog1</font>
<b>投稿者　: </b>Allen
<!-- ドメイン: 61.114.222.76 -->
URL　　 : 未登録
登録時間:2001年9月5日14時42分</pre>
本文:
<center>
<table width="95%">
<tr bgcolor="#000042"><td>
rif = Indif(Invisi,Sneak有効)<BR>
zek = dub<BR>
coldain = dub<BR>
でQuestは進められます。<BR>
<BR>
まずスタートのGiantに話し掛けて見ましょう。(Faction不足時)<BR>
<BR>
You say, 'Hail, a frost giant wolf tamer'<BR>
<BR>
a frost giant wolf tamer says 'I'm not sure I can entrust you with <BR>
this information yet.'<BR>
<BR>
か<BR>
<BR>
a frost giant wolf tamer says 'I wonder how much I could get for the <BR>
tongue of a blithering fool..leave before I decide to find out for <BR>
myself.'<BR>
<BR>
内容を教えてくれませんね＾＾；<BR>
InvisiやSneakでIndifにすれば無理やり通過できますが、クエスト的に話しを進め<BR>
て見ました。<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Factionを上げた後(Warmly以上)<BR>
<BR>
You say, 'Hail, a frost giant wolf tamer'<BR>
<BR>
a frost giant wolf tamer says 'Yes, small one?  You seek to interrupt <BR>
my work for what reason? <BR>
<BR>
反応が違いますね。<BR>
どうやら何か仕事をしているようです。<BR>
早速聞き込みを．．<BR>
<BR>
You say, 'What work'<BR>
<BR>
a frost giant wolf tamer says 'Do you not see the wolves?  I train <BR>
them.  I break them of their pride and make them into useful <BR>
servants.  Only when they willingly accept the harness are they <BR>
useful. <BR>
<BR>
You say, 'What harness'<BR>
<BR>
a frost giant wolf tamer says 'Aye.  Good metal.  We make their <BR>
harnesses and wraps here in Kael from strong black steel.  You can't <BR>
break a beast without a good strong harness.  I've learned that from <BR>
years of working with them. <BR>
<BR>
GDのColdain War Wolfから取れるWar Wolf Chokerを入手したらTamerさんにを渡<BR>
してみましょう。<BR>
<BR>
a frost giant wolf tamer says 'Ahhh.  Now this is interesting <BR>
indeed.  I see.  Crafty little ice gnats.  Here, perhaps you can find <BR>
use for one of our harnesses.  Fair trade eh?  If you want more work <BR>
let me know. <BR>
<BR>
Blood Wolf Harnessが貰えます。<BR>
（ちなみにGDのDrakkal Dire Wolfから取れる物と同一なので、それを持っていれ<BR>
ばこのステップは飛ばすことが出来ます）<BR>
<BR>
